  "texts": [
    "This study did not provide a fundamental theoretical explanation for how RAG technology improves LLM responses to breast cancer nursing care questions.",
    "The use of such LLMs in clinical settings should be conducted under the supervision of the medical staff.",
    "Finally, breast cancer knowledge is continually developing and different medical centers have varying care philosophies.",
    "Further refinement of the breast cancer knowledge base and clinical randomized controlled trials are required to validate the results of this study.",
    "As RAG technology continues to advance, its applications in clinical care are expected to increase."
